Polyamri (the Polymec Adaptive Mesh Refinement Interface) is an extension to 
the Polymec library that adds features for easily creating applications that 
use finite volume methods on adaptively refined block-structured grids. See 
the INSTALL file for details on installation.

Like that in polymec library, the source code in polyamri falls under the 
Mozilla Public License v2.0. Please see the LICENSE file for details.
